# NOTE: contracts smart-enums (src/enums/graphqlSmartEnums.ts) is deliberately COMMITTED,
# not gitignored. Although it's a codegen output, it lives in a foundation package that
# every other package consumes AS SOURCE (via tsconfig paths / jest moduleNameMapper), so
# it must be present in a fresh checkout before any typecheck/test runs. It sits alongside
# the hand-authored enums in the same directory. Regenerate + commit it when the schema changes.

